signatures.text: infix fun <T> Array<out T>.subtract( other: Iterable<T>): Set<T>
signatures.desc: Returns a set containing all elements that are contained by this array and not contained by the specified collection.

signatures.text: infix fun <T> Iterable<T>.subtract( other: Iterable<T>): Set<T>
signatures.desc: Returns a set containing all elements that are contained by this collection and not contained by the specified collection.
